Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Full Stack AI Engineer position with TechAhead. I bring over three years of professional experience in AI-powered web applications, RAG systems, and full-stack development, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

